Description: Development tools for AGI Operating System
 This package provides the complete development environment for building
 applications and system components on the AGI Operating System.
 .
 It includes header files, libraries, and tools for developing cognitive
 translators, AtomSpace-aware applications, and system-level components
 that integrate with the three-layer AGI-OS architecture.
 .
 Developers can create applications that leverage cognitive capabilities
 at the microkernel, operating system, and application layers, enabling
 unprecedented integration of AI capabilities into system software.
